data.description: Welcome home to this one of a kind property located on a large corner lot with a fenced in back yard and lots of character. The home boasts a newer roof with solar panels, a beautifully renovated kitchen with space for a breakfast area as well as having quartz countertops, upgraded cabinetry and stainless steel appliances. In the main house there are 2 bedrooms down stairs, a large bathroom, an office, oversized great room and a formal living area with the upstairs upstairs having another full bathroom as well as 2 more bedrooms. Attached to the house the owners have made a self contained mother-in-law area which has its own entrance, living area, kitchen and full bathroom so you can house a multi-family dynamic or rent it out and make some extra income. This is a home that must be seen to be appreciated.
